Muncie.Riverside Historic District (Muncie, Ind: Riverside Historic District is a national historic district located at Muncie, Delaware County, Indiana. It encompasses 74 contributing buildings and 1 contributing structure in a predominantly residential section of Muncie. The district developed between about 1895 and 1949, and includes notable examples of Colonial Revival, Tudor Revival, and Bungalow / American Craftsman style architecture.
